<br>
The Server thinks that your hit points are full (since you've successfully hidden from AE), but the Client thinks that you're hit, due to the AE icon. The Client doesn't receive an update regarding your hit points, thus, you will die.<br>
<br>
In order to fix this, you have to &quot;force&quot; the Client to update to what the Server knows. You can do this, as mentioned, by altering your hit points in some way.<br>
<br>
1. Buff yourself. the Int Caster self shielding line works well<br>
2. Nuke yourself. A Burst of Flame periodicially will update your hit points.<br>
3. Re-itemize. Take off an item that adds hit points, and put it back on again.<br>
<br>
<br>
Hope this helps.<br>
<br>
